Package: measlesr
Title: Tools for Exploring and Visualizing Global Measles Case Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Aryan", "Ajith Nair", , "ajithnai@calpoly.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Amanda", "Dong", , "amdong@calpoly.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Natalie", "Cartwright", , "nacartwr@calpoly.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Zita", "Tam", , "ztam@calpoly.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: A collection of functions for loading, summarising, and visualizing
    global measles case data sourced from the WHO via the Tidy Tuesday project
    (2025-06-24 release). Provides tools for trend analysis, detection
    method breakdowns, and country-level outbreak investigation.
